  "prompt": "What are the best places to travel outside India?",
  "response": "There are countless incredible destinations to explore outside India, each offering unique cultures, landscapes, and experiences. Here\u2019s a list of some of the best places to travel based on different interests:\n\n---\n\n### **For Nature and Scenery**\n1. **Switzerland** - Stunning Alps, pristine lakes, and picturesque villages.\n2. **New Zealand** - Dramatic landscapes, including fjords, mountains, and beaches.\n3. **Iceland** - Volcanoes, glaciers, waterfalls, and the Northern Lights.\n4. **Canada** - Rocky Mountains, national parks, and vibrant cities.\n\n---\n\n### **For Culture and History**\n1. **Italy** - Historic cities like Rome, Florence, and Venice, with art, architecture, and cuisine.\n2. **Japan** - A blend of ancient traditions and modern innovation.\n3. **Greece** - Ancient ruins, whitewashed villages, and beautiful islands.\n4. **Egypt** - Pyramids, the Nile, and a rich ancient history.\n\n---\n\n### **For Adventure**\n1. **Costa Rica** - Rainforests, wildlife, and adventure sports like zip-lining and surfing.\n2. **Nepal** - Trekking in the Himalayas, including Everest Base Camp.\n3. **South Africa** - Safari adventures, hiking, and coastal drives.\n4. **Australia** - Surfing, diving in the Great Barrier Reef, and exploring the Outback.\n\n---\n\n### **For Relaxation and Luxury**\n1. **Maldives** - Overwater bungalows, turquoise waters, and pristine beaches.\n2. **Bali, Indonesia** - Tropical vibes, wellness retreats, and lush landscapes.\n3. **France (South of France)** - Lavender fields, vineyards, and coastal towns.\n4. **Seychelles** - Secluded beaches, coral reefs, and luxury resorts.\n\n---\n\n### **For Food and Shopping**\n1. **Thailand** - Street food, night markets, and vibrant cities.\n2. **Singapore** - A food paradise with diverse cuisines and world-class shopping.\n3. **South Korea** - Delicious cuisine, lively markets, and K-pop culture.\n4. **Spain** - Tapas, wine, and vibrant festivals.\n\n---\n\n### **For Unique Experiences**\n1. **Antarctica** - A once-in-a-lifetime expedition to the frozen continent.\n2. **Morocco** - Sahara desert, medinas, and vibrant souks.\n3. **Peru** - Explore Machu Picchu and the Andes Mountains.\n4. **Dubai, UAE** - Modern architecture, desert safaris, and luxury experiences.\n\n---\n\nThese destinations cater to a variety of interests and budgets. Make sure to consider the best time to visit and any visa requirements when planning your trip! Let me know if you'd like more details about any specific destination.",
